                     └──────────┬──────────────────┘
                                │
               ┌────────────────┼────────────────┐
               │  PARALLEL      │                │
               ▼                ▼                ▼
     ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐
     │   literal    │  │   literary   │  │  technical   │
     └──────┬───────┘  └──────┬───────┘  └──────┬───────┘
            │                 │                 │
            └─────────────────┼─────────────────┘
                              │ ALL 3 returned
                              ▼
                    ┌─────────────────────┐
                    │  translation-judge   │
                    │  scores + VOTES      │
                    └──────────┬──────────┘
                               │ winner + reasoning
                               ▼
                    ┌─────────────────────┐
                    │   final result      │
                    └─────────────────────┘
```

**This is NOT a pipeline** (no sequential handoff between translators).
**This is NOT hub-and-spoke** (orchestrator doesn't pick the winner).
This is **PARALLEL generation + JUDGE VOTING** architecture.
